ROOT_NOTE=Copy apps/api/.env.example to apps/api/.env, apps/web/.env.example to apps/web/.env.local, and apps/bot/.env.example to apps/bot/.env for local development. BOT_INTERNAL_SECRET must match between apps/api and apps/bot. TELEGRAM_BOT_USERNAME should be set for deep links. Set YANDEX_MAPS_API_KEY and YANDEX_ORG_SEARCH_ENABLED=true in the API environment to import real map clubs.
